"{\n    \"Title\": \"December 31, 2013 and 2012Notes to the consolidated financial statements\",\n    \"row 1\": \"(In thousands of dollars)\",\n    \"row 2\": \"2: Significant accounting policies (continued)\",\n    \"row 3\": \"Accounts receivable\",\n    \"row 4\": \"The carrying amount of accounts receivable is reduced by a valuation allowance which is calculated on\",\n    \"row 5\": \"both a specific identification of accounts known to be delinquent and provision for aged accounts\",\n    \"row 6\": \"receivable. Management reviews the adequacy of these provisions at each reporting date. In the years\",\n    \"row 7\": \"ended December 31, 2013 and 2012 there have been no adjustments to the methodology or\",\n    \"row 8\": \"provisioning rate used by management.\",\n    \"row 9\": \"Future employee benefits\",\n    \"row 10\": \"Please see details in Note 8.\",\n    \"row 11\": \"Payment in lieu of taxes\",\n    \"row 12\": \"Please see the details in Note 10.\",\n    \"row 13\": \"Legal provisions\",\n    \"row 14\": \"Provisions are recognized when the Port Authority has a present obligation (legal or constructive) as a\",\n    \"row 15\": \"result of a past event, it is probable that the Port Authority will be required to settle the obligation, and a\",\n    \"row 16\": \"reasonable estimate can be made of the amount of the obligation.\",\n    \"row 17\": \"The amount recognized as a provision is the best estimate of the consideration required to settle the\",\n    \"row 18\": \"present obligation at the end of the reporting period, taking into account the risks and uncertainties\",\n    \"row 19\": \"surrounding the obligation.\",\n    \"row 20\": \"Please see details in Note 12.\",\n    \"row 21\": \"Tunnel concession liability\",\n    \"row 22\": \"The accounting treatment for the tunnel project including the related asset under construction and\",\n    \"row 23\": \"concession liability was a key area of judgement. Port Authority reviewed the substance of the Project\",\n    \"row 24\": \"Agreement and concluded that the present value of the tunnel\\u2019s construction costs and related liability\",\n    \"row 25\": \"should be recognized on a percentage of completion basis. See details in Note 16.\",\n    \"row 26\": \"3. Accounts receivable\",\n    \"row 27\": \"December 31, December 31, January 1,\",\n    \"row 28\": \"2013 2012 2012\",\n    \"row 29\": \"mci tN es A\",\n    \"row 30\": \"$ $ $\",\n    \"row 31\": \"Trade accounts receivable, net of allowance for\",\n    \"row 32\": \"doubtful accounts 6,305 6,227 5,113\",\n    \"row 33\": \"Airport capital assistance program receivable : - 871\",\n    \"row 34\": \"Current portion of mortgage receivable - - 66\",\n    \"row 35\": \"Deposits 12 12 12\",\n    \"row 36\": \"6,317 6,239 6,062\",\n    \"row 37\": \"eS SS SSS SSS SSS SSS SS SSS ee USSG TSNPSSURSNE nace\",\n    \"row 38\": \"Page 17\"\n}"